snippet.title: Project Wunderwaffe - War in Ukraine
snippet.description:
Add to WISHLIST on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2466030/Project_Wunderwaffe__War_in_Ukraine/

Manage new-age weapon production and the largest modern military logistical hub. 
As the alliance's Commander, you will run the world's most advanced military logistics hub and oversee the production and supply of weapons and ammunition to the front lines in Ukraine. 

#projectwunderwaffe #warinukraine #kalinka #wunderwaffe #gamedev #weaselgames #dlc
